This paper is a first attempt at a denotational semantics for \versecalc{}.
I'm using the syntax of the POPL paper, plus |hastypeKW|.

As a reminder, the syntax of \versecalc{} is given in \cref{fig:syntax}.

\section{A denotational semantics}

